        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend the Investment Advisers Act of 1940 and the Employment Retirement Income Security Act of 1974 to specify that only pecuniary factors are to be taken into account in determining best interest, and for other purposes.</title>
